{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The conversation-- mostly the conversation we could talk about and would be, where are we going?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're taking time, days and days and days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were figuring out-- I was figuring out, what these people want to do with us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So doesn't-- nothing comes out until you are there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The destination, I don't-- I was [INAUDIBLE] my conclusion that won't be good enough, you know, from seeing what is going on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the-- the SS were-- I will say, people that they want to have fights, confusion, you know, with everybody.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we weren't ready for that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were finding out not too long after what was going on, because people already knew around.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you see the documentary of ours, you see when-- when Shlomo was asking somebody.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were showing to him to see up there, you know, what was going on, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we knew that the outcome won't be good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't know at that time it was a mass killing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Didn't take too long, because I-- when they selected my-- my brother, the small brother [INAUDIBLE], seeing my mother and father going into the bus, the truck, whatever it was, he ran with them.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then after a day or two I found out that there is no coming back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we knew very fast what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were always some people, that they knew exactly that it was a killing around going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, many times we knew that our days were numbered, especially after we went to the sonderkommando, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On that-- every the six months of whatever, they used to change them, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was lucky that I was on the last one.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
